name: UPR!DELTASWAP | POC
description:
This is a proof of concept for a short demo of the AU "DELTASWAP" in game form. 

This will never be a full game by me, I just wanted to release my ideas to see what the masses think.

Want to know why I swapped certain characters and their intentions? Check out this hastily put together Swap Chart Here!

DISCLAMER

There most likely will not be any sort of content update and or expansion from me personally.

Deltarune/Undertale assets are owned by Toy fox and team
